    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Schematic drawings of Aceria cheiradeniae n. sp.: AD. Prodorsal shield; CG. Female coxigenital region; DO. Dorsal view of annuli; em. Empodium; IG. Internal female genitalia; L 1. Leg I; PV. Ventral view of posterior opisthosoma; VO. Ventral view of annuli. Scale bar: 10 μm for AD, CG, IG, PV; 5 μm for DO, L 1, VO; 2. 5 μm for em." ;
